# Build context hygiene for packages/ai/Dockerfile (built from the repo root).
# The AI image only needs packages/ai, semantic/ and data/. Everything else —
# other packages, node deps, caches, VCS — is excluded to keep the context and
# the image small and the build fast. (This is NOT .gitignore; it only scopes
# the Docker build context.)

# Other agents' packages — not needed by the AI API image.
packages/web/
packages/design-system/
packages/ingestion/
packages/transform/
packages/signals/

# Python / tooling caches and build artefacts.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/*.egg-info/
**/.venv/
**/.mypy_cache/

# Node / frontend.
**/node_modules/
**/.svelte-kit/
**/build/
**/dist/

# VCS, CI, docs, scratch.
.git/
.github/
bitacora/
docs/
*.md
!packages/ai/README.md
